    "summary": "Advocate highlights: Strong market need (20% turnover), robust technical implementation combining multiple technologies, innovative real-time coaching approach, and clear presentation. Main strengths are practical application potential and immediate market impact. Critic emphasizes: Lack of evidence/testing data, heavy reliance on existing technologies rather than proprietary solutions, potential privacy concerns, and missing concrete metrics/KPIs. Key concerns include over-dependence on AI and insufficient differentiation from existing solutions.",

