    "final_verdict": "CapAgent shows promising potential in addressing a significant market need, earning a total weighted score of 7/10. Recommendations: 1) Develop and present validation data from real-world testing 2) Address privacy and latency concerns comprehensively 3) Consider developing proprietary technologies to differentiate from competitors 4) Include specific metrics and competitive analysis in the presentation 5) Create a detailed roadmap for handling complex sales scenarios and emotional intelligence aspects. While the concept is strong, these improvements would strengthen the project's market viability."
